  <entry>
    <title>常用管理VM的Powershell組合指令</title>
    <link href="http://huawiz.github.io/2022/control-VM-with-pwsh/"/>
    <id>http://huawiz.github.io/2022/control-VM-with-pwsh/</id>
    <published>2022-07-26T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-07-28T03:30:43.588Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<html><head></head><body><p>最近工作上，常使用Hyper-V來測試環境，而每次都要按圖形介面實在有點麻煩，所以才產生這篇，來整理一下指令。</p><span id="more"></span><p>若有新組合，會不定期更新指令在這裡</p><h1 id="常用組合"><a href="#常用組合" class="headerlink" title="常用組合"></a>常用組合</h1><ol><li>自動對已經建立的主機清單，建立新的差異硬碟到指定路徑，並且設定VMList的硬碟後開啟VM</li></ol><figure class="highlight powershell hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="hljs-variable">$VMPath</span> = <span class="hljs-string">'E:\lab\test'</span> </span><br><span class="line">mkdir <span class="hljs-variable">$VMPath</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="hljs-variable">$VMParent</span> = <span class="hljs-string">'E:\VM\WinServer2019\base.vhdx'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="hljs-variable">$VMList</span> = <span class="hljs-string">"AD"</span>,<span class="hljs-string">"Server1"</span>,<span class="hljs-string">"Server2"</span>,<span class="hljs-string">"Server3"</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="hljs-keyword">Foreach</span> (<span class="hljs-variable">$VMName</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$VMList</span>){</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="hljs-variable">$VHDPath</span> = <span class="hljs-string">"<span class="hljs-variable">$</span>{VMPath}\<span class="hljs-variable">$</span>{VMName}.vhdx"</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="hljs-built_in">new-vhd</span> <span class="hljs-literal">-path</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$VHDPath</span> <span class="hljs-literal">-ParentPath</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$VMParent</span> <span class="hljs-literal">-diff</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="hljs-built_in">Set-VMHardDiskDrive</span> <span class="hljs-literal">-VMName</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$VMName</span> <span class="hljs-literal">-path</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$VHDPath</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="hljs-built_in">start-vm</span> <span class="hljs-literal">-name</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$VMName</span></span><br><span class="line">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></body></html>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p&gt;最近工作上，常使用Hyper-V來測試環境，而每次都要按圖形介面實在有點麻煩，所以才產生這篇，來整理一下指令。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
